snippet.title: Ar Tonelico 3 / Ar Tonelico Qoga - Trailer 01 [HD]
snippet.description:
[ Ar Tonelico 3 (Qoga)  ]
Trailer 01

For those who never check the website:
http://nisamerica.com/games/atq/


Wow more trailers.. this one for Ar Tonelico 3 (aka- Ar Tonelico Qoga).

Qoga is hymnos for "end/final".. pretty stupid addition to the name if you ask me, especially if the creators wanted to make Ar Tonelico 4 (which they did want to but no plans currently).

Going to speed-run this game on March when its out!

PS - And yes, there will be a Q&A video for this game too a week or two before its release.
